snippet.title: Demi Lovato Says 'Miss You' To Naya Rivera
snippet.description:
Demi Lovato is remembering the late Naya Rivera. Five months after Naya's heartbreaking death, Demi took to her Instagram to share a sweet tribute about her friend and former "Glee" costar. "Miss you," she wrote alongside a video of a bright sun.
